[{"text": "代號：5106", "conf": 0.9992485046386719, "xmin": 79.0, "xmax": 368.0, "ymin": 94.0, "ymax": 169.0, "cx": 223.5, "cy": 131.5}, {"text": "頁次：8-2", "conf": 0.9946706295013428, "xmin": 83.0, "xmax": 354.0, "ymin": 157.0, "ymax": 229.0, "cx": 218.5, "cy": 193.0}, {"text": "9", "conf": 0.9995858073234558, "xmin": 118.0, "xmax": 160.0, "ymin": 285.0, "ymax": 339.0, "cx": 139.0, "cy": 312.0}, {"text": "周護理師為避免影響到病房的安寧，會去遏止正在嬉鬧的兩位病友，當病友安靜後會獲得護理師的", "conf": 0.9993836879730225, "xmin": 209.0, "xmax": 2320.0, "ymin": 286.0, "ymax": 399.0, "cx": 1264.75, "cy": 342.25}, {"text": "稱讚，有關行為治療的原則中對周護理師的護理行為敘述，下列何者正確？", "conf": 0.9951848983764648, "xmin": 211.0, "xmax": 1804.0, "ymin": 374.0, "ymax": 470.0, "cx": 1007.5, "cy": 422.0}, {"text": "(A)正向增強", "conf": 0.9782723188400269, "xmin": 216.0, "xmax": 473.0, "ymin": 459.0, "ymax": 532.0, "cx": 344.5, "cy": 495.5}, {"text": "(B)負向增強", "conf": 0.9716294407844543, "xmin": 726.0, "xmax": 962.0, "ymin": 479.0, "ymax": 534.0, "cx": 844.0, "cy": 506.5}, {"text": "(C)相互抑制", "conf": 0.9399455189704895, "xmin": 1249.0, "xmax": 1494.0, "ymin": 477.0, "ymax": 538.0, "cx": 1371.5, "cy": 507.75}, {"text": "(D)連鎖策略", "conf": 0.9351813197135925, "xmin": 1774.0, "xmax": 2021.0, "ymin": 493.0, "ymax": 548.0, "cx": 1897.75, "cy": 520.5}, {"text": "10", "conf": 0.9999037981033325, "xmin": 99.0, "xmax": 166.0, "ymin": 541.0, "ymax": 599.0, "cx": 132.5, "cy": 569.75}, {"text": "李先生因思覺失調症而住院治療2 週，每次母親來訪就吵著要回家，致使母親生氣地說：「再吵就", "conf": 0.9822795391082764, "xmin": 216.0, "xmax": 2318.0, "ymin": 544.0, "ymax": 644.0, "cx": 1267.0, "cy": 593.75}, {"text": "不來看你了！」使得李先生擔心母親不要他了，而反覆至護理站詢問。護理師提供有關家庭互動之", "conf": 0.9944347143173218, "xmin": 219.0, "xmax": 2316.0, "ymin": 627.0, "ymax": 724.0, "cx": 1267.5, "cy": 675.5}, {"text": "護理措施，下列何者正確？①利用症狀作處理", "conf": 0.9815782308578491, "xmin": 220.0, "xmax": 1195.0, "ymin": 711.0, "ymax": 784.0, "cx": 707.5, "cy": 747.75}, {"text": "②適當支持和教導", "conf": 0.9986993670463562, "xmin": 1235.0, "xmax": 1625.0, "ymin": 726.0, "ymax": 784.0, "cx": 1430.0, "cy": 755.25}, {"text": "③著重現在情境的互動", "conf": 0.9998227953910828, "xmin": 1671.0, "xmax": 2167.0, "ymin": 738.0, "ymax": 792.0, "cx": 1919.25, "cy": 765.0}, {"text": "④採", "conf": 0.9710937738418579, "xmin": 2198.0, "xmax": 2314.0, "ymin": 743.0, "ymax": 798.0, "cx": 2256.25, "cy": 770.75}, {"text": "用家屬的方法", "conf": 0.9997923970222473, "xmin": 225.0, "xmax": 519.0, "ymin": 792.0, "ymax": 856.0, "cx": 372.0, "cy": 824.25}, {"text": "(A)①②③", "conf": 0.9712242484092712, "xmin": 222.0, "xmax": 426.0, "ymin": 871.0, "ymax": 937.0, "cx": 324.0, "cy": 904.0}, {"text": "(B)①②④", "conf": 0.9648110270500183, "xmin": 721.0, "xmax": 916.0, "ymin": 881.0, "ymax": 942.0, "cx": 818.5, "cy": 911.5}, {"text": "(C)①③④", "conf": 0.9545133709907532, "xmin": 1246.0, "xmax": 1442.0, "ymin": 888.0, "ymax": 950.0, "cx": 1344.0, "cy": 919.0}, {"text": "(D)②③④", "conf": 0.9270692467689514, "xmin": 1768.0, "xmax": 1971.0, "ymin": 901.0, "ymax": 961.0, "cx": 1869.5, "cy": 931.0}, {"text": "11", "conf": 0.9997720718383789, "xmin": 106.0, "xmax": 166.0, "ymin": 953.0, "ymax": 1007.0, "cx": 136.0, "cy": 980.0}, {"text": "有關光照療法的作用機轉之敘述，下列何者最適當？", "conf": 0.9962311387062073, "xmin": 222.0, "xmax": 1317.0, "ymin": 954.0, "ymax": 1032.0, "cx": 769.5, "cy": 993.25}, {"text": "(A)經由黏膜對光的照射", "conf": 0.9941649436950684, "xmin": 226.0, "xmax": 704.0, "ymin": 1040.0, "ymax": 1102.0, "cx": 465.0, "cy": 1071.0}, {"text": "(B)經由皮膚對光的照射", "conf": 0.9926832318305969, "xmin": 1248.0, "xmax": 1729.0, "ymin": 1057.0, "ymax": 1120.0, "cx": 1488.5, "cy": 1088.5}, {"text": "(C)經由眼睛對光的照射", "conf": 0.9826256632804871, "xmin": 229.0, "xmax": 701.0, "ymin": 1125.0, "ymax": 1181.0, "cx": 465.0, "cy": 1152.75}, {"text": "(D)經由肢體對光的照射", "conf": 0.9886330962181091, "xmin": 1248.0, "xmax": 1728.0, "ymin": 1139.0, "ymax": 1201.0, "cx": 1488.0, "cy": 1170.0}, {"text": "12", "conf": 0.9999494552612305, "xmin": 106.0, "xmax": 173.0, "ymin": 1204.0, "ymax": 1260.0, "cx": 139.5, "cy": 1232.0}, {"text": "下列何者符合環境治療的原則？", "conf": 0.9791167378425598, "xmin": 227.0, "xmax": 880.0, "ymin": 1207.0, "ymax": 1263.0, "cx": 553.75, "cy": 1235.25}, {"text": "(A)老人住院病房牆壁與地板宜採對比色，以防跌倒", "conf": 0.9959268569946289, "xmin": 227.0, "xmax": 1276.0, "ymin": 1287.0, "ymax": 1355.0, "cx": 751.5, "cy": 1321.0}, {"text": "(B)精神科病房的保護室宜採用鮮紅的顏色，以幫助情緒壓抑的病人有宣洩管道", "conf": 0.9964206218719482, "xmin": 225.0, "xmax": 1857.0, "ymin": 1364.0, "ymax": 1449.0, "cx": 1041.0, "cy": 1406.25}, {"text": "(C)精神科病房須嚴格限制病人保有私人物品，以維護病人安全", "conf": 0.9921498894691467, "xmin": 225.0, "xmax": 1510.0, "ymin": 1448.0, "ymax": 1520.0, "cx": 867.75, "cy": 1484.0}, {"text": "(D)精神科病房宜增加競爭活動，以幫助暴力病人有宣洩管道", "conf": 0.9907525181770325, "xmin": 221.0, "xmax": 1465.0, "ymin": 1529.0, "ymax": 1600.0, "cx": 843.0, "cy": 1564.5}, {"text": "情況題：張先生因攻擊行為而被家人帶來住院，入院第2 天突然出手攻擊鄰床病友，護理人員和張先生會", "conf": 0.9876525402069092, "xmin": 90.0, "xmax": 2324.0, "ymin": 1608.0, "ymax": 1695.0, "cx": 1207.25, "cy": 1651.5}, {"text": "談時，張先生表示：「他是被派來要殺我的，我很害怕！」，依此情況回答第13題至第14題。", "conf": 0.9968650341033936, "xmin": 279.0, "xmax": 2306.0, "ymin": 1692.0, "ymax": 1774.0, "cx": 1292.75, "cy": 1732.75}, {"text": "13", "conf": 0.9999463558197021, "xmin": 85.0, "xmax": 151.0, "ymin": 1772.0, "ymax": 1827.0, "cx": 118.0, "cy": 1799.5}, {"text": "護理人員對張先生之精神症狀評估，下列何項正確？", "conf": 0.9928210973739624, "xmin": 207.0, "xmax": 1305.0, "ymin": 1774.0, "ymax": 1841.0, "cx": 755.75, "cy": 1807.75}, {"text": "(A)誇大妄想", "conf": 0.9832421541213989, "xmin": 204.0, "xmax": 451.0, "ymin": 1859.0, "ymax": 1918.0, "cx": 327.75, "cy": 1888.5}, {"text": "(B)被害妄想", "conf": 0.972409725189209, "xmin": 711.0, "xmax": 954.0, "ymin": 1862.0, "ymax": 1917.0, "cx": 832.5, "cy": 1889.5}, {"text": "(C)關係妄想", "conf": 0.9674898982048035, "xmin": 1241.0, "xmax": 1480.0, "ymin": 1873.0, "ymax": 1924.0, "cx": 1360.25, "cy": 1898.5}, {"text": "(D)控制妄想", "conf": 0.9380775094032288, "xmin": 1765.0, "xmax": 2017.0, "ymin": 1874.0, "ymax": 1932.0, "cx": 1891.25, "cy": 1902.75}, {"text": "14", "conf": 0.9999473094940186, "xmin": 75.0, "xmax": 141.0, "ymin": 1937.0, "ymax": 1991.0, "cx": 108.0, "cy": 1964.0}, {"text": "護理人員對張先生的攻擊行為，在初期建立治療性關係過程中，給予的護理措施，下列何項正確？", "conf": 0.9970815777778625, "xmin": 200.0, "xmax": 2287.0, "ymin": 1943.0, "ymax": 2013.0, "cx": 1243.5, "cy": 1977.75}, {"text": "(A)提供結構性的治療環境", "conf": 0.9398053288459778, "xmin": 201.0, "xmax": 732.0, "ymin": 2031.0, "ymax": 2075.0, "cx": 466.5, "cy": 2053.0}, {"text": "(B)鼓勵病人參加支持團體", "conf": 0.9861530065536499, "xmin": 1241.0, "xmax": 1771.0, "ymin": 2035.0, "ymax": 2085.0, "cx": 1505.75, "cy": 2060.25}, {"text": "(C)提供現實感並重建認知", "conf": 0.9821146726608276, "xmin": 195.0, "xmax": 730.0, "ymin": 2109.0, "ymax": 2159.0, "cx": 462.5, "cy": 2134.0}, {"text": "(D)鼓勵使用建設性因應機轉", "conf": 0.9765433669090271, "xmin": 1240.0, "xmax": 1819.0, "ymin": 2117.0, "ymax": 2166.0, "cx": 1529.5, "cy": 2141.5}, {"text": "15", "conf": 0.9999625086784363, "xmin": 59.0, "xmax": 125.0, "ymin": 2187.0, "ymax": 2242.0, "cx": 92.0, "cy": 2214.5}, {"text": "王先生，思覺失調症，與護理師談及母親於去年辭世，隨即哈哈大笑表示很思念她。此時王先生的", "conf": 0.9917196035385132, "xmin": 185.0, "xmax": 2311.0, "ymin": 2192.0, "ymax": 2251.0, "cx": 1248.0, "cy": 2221.5}, {"text": "情緒表現最有可能為下列何者？", "conf": 0.9726638197898865, "xmin": 182.0, "xmax": 863.0, "ymin": 2273.0, "ymax": 2332.0, "cx": 522.25, "cy": 2302.75}, {"text": "(A)情感淡漠", "conf": 0.9819830060005188, "xmin": 184.0, "xmax": 433.0, "ymin": 2361.0, "ymax": 2410.0, "cx": 308.5, "cy": 2385.5}, {"text": "(B)矛盾情感", "conf": 0.9873824119567871, "xmin": 701.0, "xmax": 947.0, "ymin": 2361.0, "ymax": 2416.0, "cx": 824.0, "cy": 2388.5}, {"text": "(C)過度欣快", "conf": 0.9602252840995789, "xmin": 1234.0, "xmax": 1481.0, "ymin": 2361.0, "ymax": 2416.0, "cx": 1357.5, "cy": 2388.5}, {"text": "(D)情感低落", "conf": 0.9428969621658325, "xmin": 1762.0, "xmax": 2014.0, "ymin": 2359.0, "ymax": 2416.0, "cx": 1888.0, "cy": 2387.75}, {"text": "16", "conf": 0.9999145865440369, "xmin": 46.0, "xmax": 115.0, "ymin": 2443.0, "ymax": 2496.0, "cx": 80.5, "cy": 2469.5}, {"text": "剛入院的思覺失調症病人躲在病房角落，深信將有大批警力要捉捕他入獄。此時最適當的護理措施", "conf": 0.9915589690208435, "xmin": 175.0, "xmax": 2312.0, "ymin": 2441.0, "ymax": 2500.0, "cx": 1243.5, "cy": 2470.5}, {"text": "為下列何者？", "conf": 0.9555837512016296, "xmin": 177.0, "xmax": 471.0, "ymin": 2527.0, "ymax": 2577.0, "cx": 324.0, "cy": 2552.0}, {"text": "(A)澄清只是精神症狀並不是真的", "conf": 0.9831678867340088, "xmin": 175.0, "xmax": 869.0, "ymin": 2607.0, "ymax": 2660.0, "cx": 522.0, "cy": 2633.5}, {"text": "(B)保證警察不會進入病房", "conf": 0.9926796555519104, "xmin": 1231.0, "xmax": 1770.0, "ymin": 2602.0, "ymax": 2660.0, "cx": 1500.25, "cy": 2631.0}, {"text": "(C)接受病人此情境下的感受", "conf": 0.9589373469352722, "xmin": 175.0, "xmax": 771.0, "ymin": 2691.0, "ymax": 2744.0, "cx": 473.0, "cy": 2717.5}, {"text": "(D)鼓勵詳細描述妄想情境", "conf": 0.9936756491661072, "xmin": 1231.0, "xmax": 1769.0, "ymin": 2691.0, "ymax": 2742.0, "cx": 1500.0, "cy": 2716.5}, {"text": "17", "conf": 0.9999793767929077, "xmin": 42.0, "xmax": 105.0, "ymin": 2778.0, "ymax": 2829.0, "cx": 73.5, "cy": 2803.5}, {"text": "許小姐住院3週後自言自語頻繁，持續在床上大聲怒罵叫旁人走開，但是身邊並無其他人。用餐時", "conf": 0.9911460280418396, "xmin": 165.0, "xmax": 2302.0, "ymin": 2767.0, "ymax": 2833.0, "cx": 1233.5, "cy": 2799.75}, {"text": "間護理師叫喚許小姐多次，她才抬頭回應有人在旁一直說她的不是。此情況下，護理師最適當的護", "conf": 0.9875637292861938, "xmin": 166.0, "xmax": 2304.0, "ymin": 2847.0, "ymax": 2916.0, "cx": 1235.0, "cy": 2881.5}, {"text": "理處置為下列何者？", "conf": 0.989375114440918, "xmin": 169.0, "xmax": 617.0, "ymin": 2944.0, "ymax": 2995.0, "cx": 393.0, "cy": 2969.5}, {"text": "(B)提供現實治療", "conf": 0.989013135433197, "xmin": 1230.0, "xmax": 1568.0, "ymin": 3019.0, "ymax": 3075.0, "cx": 1399.0, "cy": 3046.75}, {"text": "(A)與醫療團隊討論，考慮調整用藥", "conf": 0.9565310478210449, "xmin": 170.0, "xmax": 916.0, "ymin": 3026.0, "ymax": 3083.0, "cx": 543.0, "cy": 3054.25}, {"text": "(D)鼓勵參加團體活動轉移註意力", "conf": 0.9719736576080322, "xmin": 1230.0, "xmax": 1908.0, "ymin": 3101.0, "ymax": 3154.0, "cx": 1568.75, "cy": 3127.75}, {"text": "(C)需立即進入保護隔離室", "conf": 0.9625885486602783, "xmin": 170.0, "xmax": 723.0, "ymin": 3109.0, "ymax": 3165.0, "cx": 446.25, "cy": 3137.25}, {"text": "思覺失調症病人出現話少表情淡漠，不願參加慢性病房團體活動，整日躺床，前述狀況最可能為下", "conf": 0.9990677237510681, "xmin": 162.0, "xmax": 2305.0, "ymin": 3169.0, "ymax": 3256.0, "cx": 1233.5, "cy": 3212.5}, {"text": "18", "conf": 0.9999428391456604, "xmin": 41.0, "xmax": 106.0, "ymin": 3198.0, "ymax": 3253.0, "cx": 73.5, "cy": 3225.5}, {"text": "列何種症狀?", "conf": 0.9245211482048035, "xmin": 166.0, "xmax": 467.0, "ymin": 3274.0, "ymax": 3334.0, "cx": 316.5, "cy": 3304.0}, {"text": "(B)負性症狀表現", "conf": 0.9910022020339966, "xmin": 697.0, "xmax": 1039.0, "ymin": 3350.0, "ymax": 3407.0, "cx": 868.0, "cy": 3378.5}, {"text": "(C)思考障礙", "conf": 0.9490588903427124, "xmin": 1228.0, "xmax": 1469.0, "ymin": 3347.0, "ymax": 3395.0, "cx": 1348.5, "cy": 3371.0}, {"text": "(D)怪異行為", "conf": 0.9733873605728149, "xmin": 1755.0, "xmax": 2003.0, "ymin": 3350.0, "ymax": 3398.0, "cx": 1879.0, "cy": 3374.0}, {"text": "(A)幻聽症狀干擾", "conf": 0.9866424202919006, "xmin": 167.0, "xmax": 533.0, "ymin": 3354.0, "ymax": 3418.0, "cx": 350.0, "cy": 3386.0}]